headline: DuPont Wins Three 2025 R&D 100 Awards
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) today announced that it has won three 2025 R&D 100 Awards in the Mechanical/Materials category. The R&D 100 Awards, sponsored by R&D World Magazine, recognizes the 100 most innovative technologies of the previous year.
